latestIgtvVideos.title: recreating bloggers' quarantine looks w @snug.style.chic
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
so this is my first collaboration for a styling video ever and who better to do it with other than the styling videos queen herself, @snug.style.chic <3
i absolutely love love @komalpandeyofficial, the way she has been producing amazing content nonstop during this quarantine and @sejalkumar1195 's new zoom call styling video and the one with ttt is SO cute! 
also loved how @caughtinacuff played with the colours in that outfit!
it was a pleasure working with riya, looking forward to doing more collaborations with her in the future, also congratulate her for hitting 25k y'all!

latestIgtvVideos.title: What To Wear | Over size tee | Chill day edition
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
um hi, it’s me the queen of inconsistency? So i thought of starting this kind of series called #whattowear and it will be mostly  around situations( eg: movies, birthday parties, dates) and sometimes a piece of clothing. So drop in some situations you’d like to see these videos about in the comments and share this video to help someone out ;)
Also shoutout to my name twinnie @aryaki._ for that fanny pack hack, what a life saver xD
